articles.title: Over 90% of people in Ireland aged over 16 are now fully vaccinated against Covid - TheJournal.ie
articles.description: It’s the highest rate in the European Union.
articles.content:
OVER 90% OF Irish people over the age of 16 are now fully vaccinated against Covid-19, the highest rate in the European Union, HSE chief executive Paul Reid has said.
